I find myself quite a knowledgeable and clever lady, also I am  very nice and responsive. I like jogging in the morning, riding my bicycle, having a picnic with my friends and family.. It seems to be foolish to describe the man whom I want to see by my side. I am looking for normal, realistic man. For me it is very important to meet my special one. Though, I can say for sure that appearance is far from being very important. 
The inner beauty is much more important than the body image. I want my man to be serious, communicative and very attentive. 

